name: H'tEph The Sun Eater: WaveXR
description:
#galacticsafari
H'tEph The Sun Eater.
Worshipped by humankind during the time of the pharaohs as the "scarab" who pushed the sun across the skies, H'tEph is actually a Klaavalian Dune Bug, the adult form of the Klaavalian Dune Larvae, having undergone metamorphosis. H'tEph The Sun Eater is unique in the metaverse for being able to directly draw energy from stars by wrapping its supernova sized mass around smaller suns. This rarely captured behavior has only been observed among the female of the species and scientists assume it has something to do with the birthing cycle, more data is required...
